A talk from the 2011 Coalition on Political Assassinations Conference. Journalist Jefferson Morley, editor of JFKFacts.org and author of Our Man in Mexico, discusses the the JFK Assassination and its connections to CIA psychological warfare operations that came before and after it. Original video came from COPA's ustream channel (no longer available).
